CustomField.description:
For Communities, the index number of the default tab. Can be a number but can often be a random multi-character string. You will need to manually click on a tab on the page to see it's code.
Also note that the code changes with every Community publishing, and Lightning Page deployment.
If a code is stored in this setting that does not match an existing tab, the browser simply strips it off.
CustomField.label: Community Page Default Tab Code
